  <refnamediv>
    <refname>formfile</refname>

    <refpurpose>Extract a file from form data</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <cmdsynopsis label="/bin/formfile" role="iosh">
      <command role="iosh">formfile</command>

      <arg choice="req"><replaceable>name</replaceable></arg>

      <arg><replaceable>path</replaceable></arg>
    </cmdsynopsis>

    <para>Extract a file keyed by <replaceable>name</replaceable> from
    multipart/form-data input.</para>

    <para>FormFile is easily chained to FormFile or Form2XML:</para>

    <para>If <replaceable>path</replaceable> is supplied then the file
    contents are saved there and the remaining parts are echoed to output.
    Otherwise the file contents are echoed to output.</para>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

